{"id":424,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":26,"title":"26. At the Customs","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":16,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs.424/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/0-26-at-the-customs.mp3","transcript":"Good morning. Can I see your passport?\nCertainly. Here it is.\nYes, that's all right. Have you got anything to declare?\nYes, I have. I've got some whisky and some cigarettes.\nHow much whisky have you got?\nA litre.\nThat's all right. And how many cigarettes have you got?\n200.\nFine. What about perfume?\nEr... No, I haven't.\nGood. Open your case, please.\nPardon?\nOpen your case, please. Open it now!\nOh, dear! Look at this!\nYou've got 3 bottles of whisky, 400 cigarettes and a lot of perfume!\nDoes that mean I can't go?","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:35","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Good morning. Can I see your passport?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/1.mp3","time_start":2.16,"time_end":4.23},{"position":2,"content":"Certainly. Here it is.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/2.mp3","time_start":4.26,"time_end":5.72},{"position":3,"content":"Yes, that's all right. Have you got anything to declare?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/3.mp3","time_start":5.88,"time_end":9.22},{"position":4,"content":"Yes, I have. I've got some whisky and some cigarettes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/4.mp3","time_start":9.28,"time_end":12.91},{"position":5,"content":"How much whisky have you got?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/5.mp3","time_start":12.91,"time_end":14.18},{"position":6,"content":"A litre.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/6.mp3","time_start":14.33,"time_end":15.15},{"position":7,"content":"That's all right. And how many cigarettes have you got?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/7.mp3","time_start":15.35,"time_end":18.08},{"position":8,"content":"200.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/8.mp3","time_start":18.18,"time_end":19.33},{"position":9,"content":"Fine. What about perfume?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/9.mp3","time_start":19.49,"time_end":21.52},{"position":10,"content":"Er... No, I haven't.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/10.mp3","time_start":21.59,"time_end":23.68},{"position":11,"content":"Good. Open your case, please.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/11.mp3","time_start":23.75,"time_end":26.23},{"position":12,"content":"Pardon?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/12.mp3","time_start":26.23,"time_end":26.92},{"position":13,"content":"Open your case, please. Open it now!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/13.mp3","time_start":27.01,"time_end":29.81},{"position":14,"content":"Oh, dear! Look at this!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/14.mp3","time_start":29.97,"time_end":31.65},{"position":15,"content":"You've got 3 bottles of whisky, 400 cigarettes and a lot of perfume!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/15.mp3","time_start":31.65,"time_end":36.42},{"position":16,"content":"Does that mean I can't go?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/26-at-the-customs-2022-03-07-21-13-03/16.mp3","time_start":36.56,"time_end":38.14}]}